        <mxCell id="title" value="muoidv Lab — Architecture Overview (1 region ap-southeast-1, 2 AZ, 1 env)" style="text;html=1;align=center;fontSize=18;fontStyle=1;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="20" y="10" width="1660" height="30" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>

        <mxCell id="legend" value="Numbered flow:&#10;(1) User → Route53 resolve *.muoidv.do2602.click&#10;(2) → ALB:443 (ACM wildcard cert)  → target group pod (LBC tạo ALB từ Ingress)&#10;(3) Pod app → PostgreSQL pod (cluster DNS: postgresql.database.svc.cluster.local:5432)&#10;(4) Worker node pull image: ECR → VPC Endpoint Interface (api+dkr, no NAT)  &#10;(5) Worker node S3 layer/yum → S3 Gateway Endpoint (free)&#10;(6) External pull (DockerHub/Bitnami) → NAT GW → IGW (chỉ khi cần)&#10;(7) Jenkins build → push ECR → kubectl apply (in-cluster ServiceAccount)&#10;(8) Jenkins clone code → GitHub PAT (HTTPS qua NAT)" style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=top;fontSize=11;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=0;fillColor=#fff2cc;strokeColor=#d6b656;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="1170" y="50" width="510" height="180" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>

