        <mxCell id="cost" value="💰 Cost dự kiến chạy LIVE 24/7:&#10;• EKS control plane: $0.10/h × 24 = $2.4/ngày&#10;• MNG t3.medium × 2: ~$1.5/ngày&#10;• NAT GW: $1.08/ngày + traffic&#10;• ALB: ~$0.6/ngày × 4 ALB (pgadmin/jenkins/sample/grafana) — DÙNG IngressGroup gộp 1 ALB → ~$0.6/ngày&#10;• EBS gp3 PVC: ~$0.03/ngày&#10;• VPC Endpoint Interface ECR: ~$0.5/ngày&#10;TỔNG ~$6/ngày — tắt MNG ban đêm để tiết kiệm" style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=top;fontSize=11;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=0;fillColor=#f8cecc;strokeColor=#b85450;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="1170" y="250" width="510" height="170" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>

        <mxCell id="seq" value="📋 Thứ tự build (10 sub-comp):&#10;1️⃣ VPC custom (2 AZ × public+private + IGW + NAT + RT) — Console &quot;VPC and more&quot;&#10;2️⃣ EKS cluster v1.34 attach VPC + MNG 2 node (Console wizard 6 step Custom)&#10;3️⃣ AWS Load Balancer Controller (Helm + IRSA + iam_policy.json)&#10;4️⃣ NAT GW route + VPC Endpoint S3/ECR (đã làm 1 phần ở step 1, hoàn thiện)&#10;5️⃣ EBS CSI Add-on + StorageClass gp3 default&#10;6️⃣ Bitnami PostgreSQL ns database (Helm pull + values-edit.yaml)&#10;7️⃣ pgAdmin4 + Ingress ALB + ACM wildcard cert + R53 record&#10;8️⃣ Sample app tvtien-chart (helm create) + Ingress&#10;9️⃣ Jenkins + GitHub PAT + ECR cred + K8s connect + pipeline thật&#10;🔟 kube-prometheus-stack (BONUS) + Grafana Ingress" style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=top;fontSize=11;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=0;fillColor=#d5e8d4;strokeColor=#82b366;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="1170" y="440" width="510" height="240" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>

